<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Project Manager</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="sidebar">
      <h4>CRL Project Manager</h4>

      <a class="active" href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
      <a href="/team">Team</a>
      <a href="#about-section">About CRL</a>
      <a href="#vision-section">Our Vision</a>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container bg-image">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="title">
          <h1>Welcome to the CRL Project Manager</h1>
          <p>Your project management tool to keep everything on track.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-container">
          <button onclick="openProjectForm()">Create New Project</button>
          <button onclick="openTeamForm()">Create New Team</button>
        </div>

        <div class="image-container">
          <img src="/images/crl.png" alt="CRL Logo" />
        </div>

        <div class="about-crl" id="about-section">
          <br />
          <h4>About CRL (GAD)</h4>
          <p>
            The lush green campus of Central Research Laboratory, Ghaziabad
            (CRL-GAD) is located in Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh. It has been
            established with the following objectives:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              To generate new ideas and concepts that can result in new or
              improved products.
            </li>
            <li>
              Examine emerging concepts and technologies and adapt them for new
              products and systems.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="vision-container" id="vision-section">
          <h2><i>Our Vision</i></h2>
          <p>
            Our vision is to empower teams to achieve their highest potential
            through efficient project management tools that streamline
            processes, foster collaboration, and drive innovation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
